      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"1. SO REFINED proved too good on debut over 350m at this track to score by 6 lengths (20.08). Can use the low draw to advantage. Looks the one to beat. 6. CHOPPER SURE CAN hit the ground running last start and was never headed (20.37) at this track in Maiden over 350m. Form should stack up. 2. LEN TANK settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 5th (26.01) at this track. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Has ability and is one of the better chances. 7. WORDS OF WISDOM was strongly fancied last time on the back of a win two back but could only manage fourth (20.44) at this track.\",\"runners\":[1,6,2,7],\"exclusive\":false}",
